text: Sai Yinjirigala or Saiyinjirigala (Mongolian: Sainjargal, ; born 4 December 1989 in Zhenglan Banner, Inner Mongolia) is a Southern Mongol male judoka from China. He represented China at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. ==References== == External links == * * * * * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of China Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:People from Xilingol League Category:Sportspeople from Inner Mongolia Category:Southern Mongol sportspeople
